As with other locations, the type annotation is optional, but will be an implicit any if not specified.与其他地方一样，类型注解是可选的，如果没有指定，将会是任意类型。Fields can also have initializers; these will run automatically when the class is instantiated:字段也可以有初始值，这会在类被实例化时自动运行：
