&#125;

const pt &#x3D; new Point();
&#x2F;&#x2F; Prints 0, 0
console.log(&#96;$&#123;pt.x&#125;, $&#123;pt.y&#125;&#96;);

Just like with const, let, and var, the initializer of a class property will be used to infer its type:和 const，let，var 类型推断的初始值。
