  &#x2F;&#x2F; Not initialized, but no error
  name!: string;
&#125;

readonlyFields may be prefixed with the readonly modifier. This prevents assignments to the field outside of the constructor.字段可以使用 readonly 前缀。这将阻止在构造函数之外赋值给字段。
