Note that a field-backed get&#x2F;set pair with no extra logic is very rarely useful in JavaScript. It’s fine to expose public fields if you don’t need to add additional logic during the get&#x2F;set operations.&gt;注意，没有额外逻辑的字段-获取/设置-对偶在 JavaScript 中很少是有用的。如果您不需要在获取/设置操作期间添加额外逻辑，则可以暴露公共字段。
