WARNING
It’s important to understand that an implements clause is only a check that the class can be treated as the interface type. It doesn’t change the type of the class or its methods at all. A common source of error is to assume that an implements clause will change the class type - it doesn’t!implements 语句仅仅检查类是否按照接口类型实现，但它并不会改变类的类型或者方法的类型。一个常见的错误就是以为 implements 语句会改变类的类型,——然而实际上它并不会：

